# 1. Date Formats

| Format | Meaning               | Example Output |
| ------ | --------------------- | -------------- |
| `%Y`   | Year (4 digits)       | `2026`         |
| `%y`   | Year (2 digits)       | `26`           |
| `%m`   | Month (01-12)         | `06`           |
| `%B`   | Full month name       | `June`         |
| `%b`   | Short month name      | `Jun`          |
| `%d`   | Day of month (01-31)  | `25`           |
| `%j`   | Day of year (001-366) | `176`          |

# 2. Weekday Formats

| Format                      | Meaning                        | Example Output |
| --------------------------- | ------------------------------ | -------------- |
| `%A`                        | Full weekday name              | `Thursday`     |
| `%a`                        | Short weekday name             | `Thu`          |
| `%w`                        | Weekday as number (`0=Sunday`) | `4`            |
| `%u` *(platform-dependent)* | Weekday (`1=Monday`)           | `4`            |


# 3. Time Formats

| Format | Meaning               | Example Output |
| ------ | --------------------- | -------------- |
| `%H`   | Hour (24-hour, 00-23) | `14`           |
| `%I`   | Hour (12-hour, 01-12) | `02`           |
| `%M`   | Minute (00-59)        | `37`           |
| `%S`   | Second (00-59)        | `52`           |
| `%f`   | Microseconds          | `456732`       |
| `%p`   | AM / PM               | `PM`           |


# 4. Time Zone

| Format | Meaning       | Example Output |
| ------ | ------------- | -------------- |
| `%Z`   | Timezone name | `IST`          |
| `%z`   | UTC offset    | `+0530`        |



# 5. Common Combined Formats

| Format         | Output                   |
| -------------- | ------------------------ |
| `%d/%m/%Y`     | `25/06/2026`             |
| `%d-%m-%Y`     | `25-06-2026`             |
| `%Y-%m-%d`     | `2026-06-25`             |
| `%d-%b-%Y`     | `25-Jun-2026`            |
| `%B %d, %Y`    | `June 25, 2026`          |
| `%A, %d %B %Y` | `Thursday, 25 June 2026` |
| `%H:%M:%S`     | `14:37:52`               |
| `%I:%M:%S %p`  | `02:37:52 PM`            |


# 6. Special Formats

| Format | Meaning                      | Example                          |
| ------ | ---------------------------- | -------------------------------- |
| `%%`   | Prints `%`                   | `%`                              |
| `%c`   | Complete date & time         | `Thu Jun 25 14:37:52 2026`       |
| `%x`   | Locale's date representation | `06/25/26` *(depends on locale)* |
| `%X`   | Locale's time representation | `14:37:52` *(depends on locale)* |


