### Easy Memory Trick

| Lowercase | Meaning       | Uppercase | Meaning       |
| --------- | ------------- | --------- | ------------- |
| `%m`      | **m**onth     | `%M`      | **M**inute    |
| `%b`      | short month   | `%B`      | full month    |
| `%a`      | short weekday | `%A`      | full weekday  |
| `%y`      | 2-digit year  | `%Y`      | 4-digit year  |
| `%I`      | 12-hour clock | `%H`      | 24-hour clock |